height: 32px; background: {{primaryColor}}; color: white; border-radius: 50%; text-align: center; line-height: 32px; font-weight: bold; margin-right: 12px;\">3</div></td><td><strong style=\"color: #1F2937; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; font-size: 16px;\">Start Trading</strong><span style=\"color: #6B7280; font-size: 14px;\">Buy your first cryptocurrency</span></td></tr></table></div><div style=\"text-align: center; margin: 32px 0;\"><a href=\"{{dashboardUrl}}\" style=\"display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #06B6D4 0%, #0891B2 100%); color: white; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 32px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;\">Get Started Now</a></div>"
